Exercise Question 3: Create child class Bus that will inherit all of the variables and methods of the Vehicle class

Given:
class Vehicle:

    def __init__(self, name, max_speed, mileage):
        self.name = name
        self.max_speed = max_speed
        self.mileage = mileage
        
 Create a Bus object that will inherit all of the variables and methods of the Vehicle class and display it.
 
 Expected Output:
 Vehicle Name: School Volvo Speed: 180 Mileage: 12
